data.description: Location, location, location!  This property offering 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a two car attached garage and numerous other rooms for private office, a recreation room, living and family room and plenty of space to add a bathroom and have additional bedrooms downstairs.  The home has a gas fireplace in the dining area and another fireplace in the Great Room offering highly efficient heat sources in addition to natural gas. The lot is .39 and boasts a lovely, private, fenced backyard with views of Northstar and the Sierra Crest.  Bring your toys as additional parking bad and access to the side-yard to store your RV or boat!  The home is in a coveted year-around neighborhood walking distance to Meadow Park, shopping, restaurants and Truckee High School.  There is no HOA in this neighborhood and minutes off the freeway and close to numerous ski resorts and golf courses including Sugar Bowl, Boreal, Palisades Tahoe, Northstar, Tahoe Donner and Coyote Moon.  This location is also prime access to access Interstate 80 coming from the Bay Area or Reno.
